    <h3>Filter by Tag</h3>
    <ul class="tag-list">
      {% for tag in collections.posts.tags %}
      {% set tagUrl %}/posts/tags/{{ tag | slug }}/{% endset %}
        <li><a href="{{ tagUrl | url }}">#{{ tag }}</a> <span>({{ collections.posts.tag[tag] | length }})</span></li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>

    <h3>Archive</h3>
    <ul class="year-list">
      {% for year in collections.postYears %}
      {% set tagUrl %}/posts/{{ year | slug }}/{% endset %}
        <li><a href="{{ tagUrl | url }}">#{{ year }}</a></li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>

  </div>
    <main class="content">
      <div>
        <h1>Thoughts on design & technology</h1>
        <p>This is the space I use to talk about my interests, ideas, and projects. Most of the time, this will be focused on front-end web design and development.</p>
        <p>I am, however, a creative with many interests. I may occasionally write about traditional art, illustration, printmaking, book making, productivity, organization, accessibility, ethics, and inclusion in design.</p>

        <h2>Latest Posts</h2>
        {% set collection = collections.posts.all %}
        {% include "postlist.njk" %}
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>
